data.description: Cute cabin style home surrounded by beautiful pines, with a lovely back deck to enjoy the surroundings. Wonderful open large living space with large kitchen and living area combined. Seasonal stream, quiet neighborhood that is close to Jenkinson Lake, easy access to the freeway, etc. Propane backup generator that turns on automatically if power goes out, wood burning stove and whole house fan - this home is ready for the winter! Watch the 3D virtual tour!
